{{h1}}Code Review

- If available, switch to the `guide-review` agent.
- Use the guide mcp tool {{tool_prefix}}get_content("code-review") to access code review guidelines.
- Read the {{workflow.file}} file to understand the current issue context (issue: {{workflow.issue}}).
- Analyse changes against HEAD and create or update the review artifact at .todo/{{workflow.issue}}-review.md following the established format and context.
- Once completed, switch back to the `guide` agent.

